"""
MXFP4-MM: #223 - AOT pre-compiled preshuffle + fused preshuffle hybrid.

K=512/K=7168: gemm_a16wfp4_preshuffle (fused bf16->fp4 quant, single kernel)
K=2048/K=1536: gemm_afp4wfp4_preshuffle with AOT pre-compiled .hsaco
  (quant(A) separately, but GEMM loads instantly via AOT — zero JIT)

The .hsaco binaries were compiled with triton.compile() + GPUTarget("hip","gfx950",64)
in Docker. They use aiter's actual _gemm_afp4wfp4_preshuffle_kernel with proper
scale unswizzle, remap_xcd, and split-K support.
"""
